    "Traditionally this is a multi-stage process of calling, merging, genotyping and re-merging 21, 52, 53.",
    "This is clearly inefficient as the BAM/CRAM alignment files need to be assessed twice.",
    "Even so, this process can be achieved only by using a few of the existing methods (SVJedi 54, Sniffles 28 and cuteSV 47).",
    "The Sniffles2 strategy requires only an initial calling and merging to obtain a fully genotyped population-level VCF.",
    "Figure 1b illustrates the principle."
  ],
